Package: phybaseR
Type: Package
Title: R functions to easily create and run PhyBaSE models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Achaz", "von Hardenberg",
      email = "achaz.hardenberg@unipv.it",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools for specifying and fitting Phylogenetic Bayesian 
    Structural Equation Models (PhyBaSE) using JAGS. PhyBaSE models allow causal
    inference in phylogenetic comparative analyses, accounting for phylogenetic
    uncertainty and handling missing data. Implements the methods described in
    von Hardenberg and Gonzalez-Voyer (2025) <doi:10.1111/2041-210X.70044>.
